title: Iron Man - The Armor Wars I and II, John Romita and John Byrne C
description:
All digital Iron Man collection that focuses on the artist / writer John Byrne as well as the artist John Romita Jr.

It deviates a bit by including the Armour Wars One, but includes the storylines of the late '70s through the '90s that influenced the Iron Man movies.

Note: I altered some pages in Photoshop for purposes of story flow. The official releases of issues 264 and 266 did a less than ideal job of presenting pages 11 and 10, respectively.

If you want these particular rips, look here: Hitlist week 2014.03.12 Part 4
